 true, with US support waxing and waning. A detailed appendix, exploring political murder country by country, provides an additional resource for readers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAssassination -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aAssassinationzLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aDisappeared persons -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aDisappeared personszLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aMassacres -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aMassacreszLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aMurder -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aMurderzLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical culturezLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical persecution -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aPolitical persecutionzLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical violence -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aPolitical violencezLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 0aState-sponsored terrorism -- Latin America -- History -- 20th century. 0aState-sponsored terrorismzLatin AmericaxHistoryy20th century. 4aAnthropology and Archaeology : Anthropology. 4aHistory : History. 4aLatin American, Caribbean, and Latinx Studies : Latin American Studies. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Science. 4aSociology : Sociology. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143845665240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438456652423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438456652/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles